title: At The Center Pt. 4 ~ Bobby Hutcherson from coast to coast
description:
Vibraphone legend Bobby Hutcherson talks about his long hostory with Blue Note Records, from working with Jackie McLean in NYC, to reconnecting with Harold Land on the West Coast. Check out more video shorts with the NEA Jazz Master, former SFJAZZ Collective member and long-time San Francisco native!

For more videos, subscribe today to the SFJAZZ YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/SFJAZZOnline
